[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amaze</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Amaze
<hw>A*maze"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>Bewilderment, arising from fear,
surprise, or wonder; amazement.</def> <mark>[Chiefly poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The wild, bewildered⟦br⟧
Of one to stone converted by <qex>amaze</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Byron.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amazedly</ent>⟦br⟧
